    Scope and Contents
This file consists of meeting minutes, correspondence, memoranda, cassette tapes &amp; reports.  Meeting minute topics include President's decisions to Tenure, Board member selection and Tenure appeal decisions.  Correspondnece is from various Board members to the Board of Regens and SSU community.  The cassette tapes are of the Appeals Board and the subject is the David Sanford negative tenure decision case.  Reports include draft of University appelas board procedures.
Records under C2/2/12, 13, 14, &amp; 15 are closely related.  
  
